extends ./layout/base-lu.pug

block title
  title Edit comment on Amsterdam meetup

block content

  .row.margin-top-l

    .col-sm-8

      h4.section-title Edit comment

      form(action="comment.html")
        .card
          .card-body
            .media
              .media-left
                a(href="my-stream.html")
                  img.media-object.img-circle.img-medium(src='content/images/avatar1.jpg')
              .media-body
                .media-heading.text-m
                  a(href="my-stream.html") John Johnson
                  .text-gray-lighter 6 hours ago

                .form-group
                  textarea.form-control.form-control--autogrow.js-textarea-autogrow(placeholder='Write a comment...', data-min-rows="4") We know that not paying speakers and not covering speaker expenses causes events to become less diverse. The ability to give time, energy and professional skills free of charge is a privilege. 
        .form-group.clearfix
          button.btn.btn-primary.pull-right(type='submit') Submit
